data-triple-N3.o: "USA Network (commonly referred to as USA) is an American cable television channel launched in 1971. Once a minor player in basic cable, the network has steadily gained popularity due to original programming, including initial hits such as Silk Stalkings and La Femme Nikita, which were gradually followed by Monk, Psych, White Collar, Suits, Burn Notice, Royal Pains, and other series. The network is also known for having a relationship with WWE Raw."@en
